  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK456">
<l>maṉamtūyārk keccanaṉ ṟāku miṉantūyārk</l>
<l>killainaṉ ṟākā viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the pure-minded there will be a good posterity. By those whose associates are pure, no deeds will be done that are not good.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
